branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The CRA1 rack &amp; pinion rotary actuator offers very high torque-to-size and accurate positioning. Bore sizes are 30, 50, 63, 80 and 100mm. Units may be ordered auto-switch capable and with cushions. Dimensions range from 3&quot; X 4&quot; X 2&quot; to a maximum of 8&quot; X 9.65&quot; X 4.41&quot;. Single shaft end or double shaft end models are available.
&lt;/p&gt;

